input_str: Service, location, comfort: just some of the things that are critical to a hotel’s success. However, in a digital age in which social media presence counts for just as much as how well the bedsheets are tucked in, Insta-friendliness is an important factor in keeping the travellers coming. In its 2017 Year in Review, Instagram has revealed that Singapore’s Marina Bay Sands has its social media aesthetics on lockdown, ranking first among the 10 most Instragmmed hotels
